{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"points","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/points","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n\n<p><code>points</code>属性定义了用来画一个<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polyline\"><code>&lt;polyline&gt;</code></a>元素或画一个 SVGElement(\"polygon\") }}元素的点的数列。</p>\n\n<p>每个点用用户坐标系统中的一个 X 坐标和 Y 坐标定义。用逗号分开每个点的 X 和 Y 坐标标记是一个常用实践（但是并非必要），使用空间标注每个点。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">类别</th>\n   <td>无</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">值</th>\n   <td>&lt;list-of-points&gt;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">可变性</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">规范文档</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/shapes.html#PolylineElementPointsAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): The polyline element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/shapes.html#PolygonElementPointsAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): The polygon element</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2000/svg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">version</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>1.1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>polygon</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">points</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>100,10 250,150 200,110<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n           <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>fill:lime;stroke:purple;stroke-width:1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>svg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下元素可以使用<code>points</code>属性：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polyline\"><code>&lt;polyline&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polygon\"><code>&lt;polygon&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考主页","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"points","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"points","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"points","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/points","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/points/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/z